  "keyFeatures": [
    "Durable workflow orchestration with state persistence",
    "Event-driven architecture with Apache Pulsar",
    "Automatic retry and timeout handling",
    "Multiple storage backends (Redis, MySQL, PostgreSQL)",
    "Tag-based workflow and task management",
    "CloudEvents integration for observability",
    "Dashboard for monitoring and debugging",
    "Flexible configuration with YAML or builders"
